      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Jumpbox-resources.json<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: When enabled, is responsible for deploying all resources related to the Jumpbox VM, the one with a public IP address that can be used to access MongoDB cluster from public network."
